        "created_at": "2022-01-15T14:19:31.017Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I have a fdb cluster and lost all transaction nodes and 10% storage node by accidentally removing data directory , is there any way to bring it back to work? It is acceptable to lose some data.</p>\n<p>fdb version is 6.0.15</p>\n<p>Thanks in advance.</p>",
